&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT IMMUNEFI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Immunefi is the world’s leading crowdsourced security platform for the digital economy. We protect over $180 billion in onchain assets by connecting the most skilled ethical hackers on the planet with the protocols that need them. Our products — Bug Bounty Programs, Managed Triage, and Audit Competitions — are the de facto security infrastructure for serious blockchain protocols worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
