&lt;li&gt;Respond to community queries, resolve issues, and escalate feedback to relevant teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure timely communication of platform updates, new initiatives, and community-focused opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and share engaging content tailored for the Discord community, including FAQs, tutorials, and announcements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
