&lt;li&gt;Managed Triage (MTS): Immunefi reviews and triages incoming vulnerability reports on the client’s behalf.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audit Competitions: Time-boxed, incentivized competitive audits that surface vulnerabilities at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All contracts are annual or multi-year (no monthly rolling); we actively push for multi-year agreements with discounting as the incentive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
